# 1. Local Database & Storage (Crucial!)
# Never commit your local database files or binary state to GitHub
*.db
*.db-journal

# 2. Go Compiled Binaries & Executables
# This blocks compiled files from cluttering your repository
main
my_server
*.exe
*.exe~
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib

# 3. VS Code & IDE Configuration Directories
# Keeps your personal editor window sizes and settings out of the workspace
.vscode/
.idea/
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.swp

# 4. OS-Specific System Files
# Prevents Mac and Windows system clutter
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db